  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The Diagrammatics of \u2018Race\u2019 (2024), published by Open Book Publishers. 3048 downloads \u2014 actief gebruik. 8 citation(s) \u2014 early signal.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The Diagrammatics of \u2018Race\u2019 was published by Open Book Publishers in 2024. Conceptually, the work connects to Kinship, Family tree, Race (biology), Humanity and Ideology.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">OpenAlex records 8 citations. Citations peaked in 2026 with 6 citing works. Notable citing venues include Evolutionary Biology/Evolutionary biology, History, philosophy and theory of the life sciences and Prace Kulturoznawcze. Inferred role: Scholarly uptake.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">3048 recorded downloads via open-access infrastructure.</p>",
